text: Dominik Malý (born 24 January 1996) is a Slovak footballer who currently plays for Slovan Bratislava II as a midfielder. ==Club career== ===FK Senica=== Malý made his professional Fortuna Liga's debut for FK Senica on 3 October 2014 against FK Dukla Banská Bystrica.SENICA VS.
